This was one of the first things I'd ever written in Ruby back in 2005. 

It's a port of the GEO::StreetAddress::US Perl Library. http://search.cpan.org/~sderle/Geo-StreetAddress-US-0.99/US.pm

Please feel free to do whatever you'd like with it, and if you find it useful let me know.

